    • getCovidObservations

      @NotNull public static Set<UkbObservation> getCovidObservations(Collection<UkbObservation> labObservations, InputCodeSettings inputCodeSettings)
      Filter a list of UkbObservation resources to those describing a covid PCR finding.
      Parameters:
      labObservations - A list with observation resources.
      inputCodeSettings - An InputCodeSettings instance that contains the valid covid pcr loinc codes.
      Returns:
      A filtered collection containing only observations with covid pcr findings. If the input list is null it will return an empty set.

    • getObservationsByValue

      @NotNull public static Set<UkbObservation> getObservationsByValue(Collection<UkbObservation> covidObservations, CoronaFixedValues obsResultType)
      Filtering a list of covid UkbObservation resources on a result in the Observation.getValue() field.
      Parameters:
      covidObservations - A filtered list with observation resources, that describe covid findings. Creatable via getCovidObservations(Collection, InputCodeSettings).
      obsResultType - The value to filter on (e.g. CoronaFixedValues.POSITIVE).
      Returns:
      A filtered collection containing the resources that have the specified result type in the Observation.getValue() attribute.
